name: $UDI
desc: An identifier affixed to an item by the manufacturer when it is first made, where each item has a different identifier.

name: $SNO
desc: An identifier issued by a governmental organization to an individual for the purpose of the receipt of social services and benefits.

name: $SB
desc: The identifier associated with the person or service that requests or places an order.

name: $PLAC
desc: The Identifier associated with the person, or service, who produces the observations or fulfills the order requested by the requestor.
